 Core Application

Backend Framework:

Spring Boot (Microservices architecture)


Frontend Framework:

React.js


Database:

MySQL (Relational DB for structured data)


API Gateway:

Spring Cloud Gateway


Security:

Spring Security + JWT/OAuth 2.0




✅ Real-Time & Event-Driven

Apache Kafka → For event streaming (notifications, status updates, inter-service communication)
Spring WebSocket → For real-time chat and live dashboard updates


✅ File Handling & PDF Processing

Apache Tika → Extract text from PDFs for keyword search
Apache PDFBox → Validate and manipulate PDF files
MinIO → Open-source S3-compatible storage for resumes
ClamAV → Open-source antivirus for scanning uploaded files


✅ AI & NLP (Open Source)

spaCy → Resume parsing (skills, experience extraction)
HuggingFace Transformers → Semantic matching for candidate-job fit
Tesseract OCR → For scanned PDF text extraction (if needed)


✅ Search & Ranking

Elasticsearch → Fast candidate/job search and filtering
Sentence-BERT (via HuggingFace) → Intelligent skill matching


✅ Caching & Performance

Redis → In-memory cache for sessions, availability slots, and notifications


✅ Notifications

Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM) → Push notifications
SMTP (Postfix or SendGrid free tier) → Email notifications
Twilio Free Tier → SMS alerts (optional)


✅ Video Interview Integration

WebRTC → Open-source video calling
Jitsi Meet API → Free video conferencing integration


✅ Deployment & Scalability

Docker + Kubernetes (K8s) → Containerization and orchestration
Prometheus + Grafana → Monitoring and analytics


✅ Security & Compliance

Spring Security + JWT/OAuth 2.0 → Role-based access control
OWASP Dependency Check → Vulnerability scanning


✅ Frontend Enhancements

PDF.js → Preview resumes in browser
Open-source Chat UI → For internal ticket chat (WhatsApp-style)
